briefing.en-US: Secretive Automaton mining operations are underway. Repatriate the state-of-the-art habitat technologies that make these operations possible, and hold Outpost Alpha until this tech can be used to expand it into a spore-proof subterranean haven.
briefing.de-DE: Es laufen geheime Roboter-Bergbauaktivitäten. Holen Sie die hochmodernen Habitat-Technologien zurück, die diese Operationen ermöglichen, und halten Sie Außenposten Alpha, bis der mit dieser Technologie zu einem sporenfesten unterirdischen Zufluchtsort erweitert werden kann.
briefing.es-ES: Hay operaciones de extracción secretas de los autómatas en curso. Repatriad la tecnología de hábitat innovadora que posibilita estas operaciones y mantened el puesto de avanzada alfa hasta que esta tecnología pueda usarse para expandirse como puerto subterráneo a prueba de esporas.
briefing.ru-RU: Автоматоны тайно добывают полезные ископаемые. Верните передовые технологии создания обитаемых сред, которые позволяют врагу вести добычу, и удерживайте аванпост «Альфа» до завершения работ по превращению его в защищенный от спор подземный рай.
briefing.fr-FR: Les automatons mènent une opération d'extraction minière secrète. Rapatriez les innovations architecturales révolutionnaires qui permettent ces opérations et gardez le contrôle de l'avant-poste Alpha, jusqu'à ce que nous puissions utiliser cette technologie pour créer un havre souterrain imperméable aux spores.
briefing.it-IT: Sono in corso operazioni minerarie segrete degli Automaton. Recuperare le tecnologie abitative di nuova generazione che rendono possibili tali operazioni e difendere l'Avamposto Alfa fino a che queste tecnologie non potranno essere usate per trasformarlo in un rifugio sotterraneo a prova di spore.
briefing.pl-PL: Automaty przeprowadzają tajne operacje wydobywcze. Operacje te są możliwe dzięki nowoczesnym technologiom osadniczym. Musimy je przejąć, utrzymać posterunek Alfa i użyć technologii, aby zbudować podziemne schronienie odporne na zarodniki.
briefing.zh-Hans: 机器人正在秘密开展采矿作业。收回支援采矿作业的尖端栖息地技术，并守住阿尔法哨站，直至该技术能够将哨站扩建为没有孢子侵袭的地下避难所为止。
briefing.zh-Hant: 機器人正在進行祕密採礦作業。拿回讓這些作業得以進行的尖端棲地技術，並守住阿爾法前哨站，直到能運用該技術將其擴建為防孢子地下避風港。

name.ja-JP: フェルカド・セカンダス

biome.name: Basic Swamp
biome.description: Tall, gnarled trees flourish across the surface of this forested world. Sunlight filters past dangling vines, to the saturated undergrowth below.

hazards.name: None
hazards.description: This planet's environment is not yet known, or has no environmental modifiers.

biome.name: Scorched Moor
biome.description: Scorching temperatures, high winds, and low precipitation cause a near-constant cycle of fires to sweep this planet, punctuated by short bursts of lush rebirth between infernos.

hazards.name: Fire Tornadoes
hazards.description: Planet is ravaged by deadly fire tornadoes.

biome.name: Acidic Badlands
biome.description: Dense, toxic fumes from deep within the planet's crust seep out of cracks in the earth and coat the ground in a sickly haze.

hazards.name: Acid Storms
hazards.description: Corrosive acid storms temporarily reduce armor effectiveness for both enemy and friendly units.

biome.name: Deadlands
biome.description: The lifeless grey of this planet is interrupted only by the violet flowers that grow from strange, parasitic outcroppings.

hazards.name: Thick Fog
hazards.description: Dense fog lightly reduce visibility for both enemy and friendly units.

biome.name: Desert Dunes
biome.description: A blazing-hot desert planet, its rocky mesas are the sole interruptions to the endless sea of dunes.

hazards.name: Sandstorms
hazards.description: Dense sandstorms reduce mobility and greatly reduce visibility for both enemy and friendly units.

biome.name: Ionic Jungle
biome.description: The strange subversion of photosynthesis that sustains the oddly-hued flora that flourishes on this planet remains an intriguing mystery to Super Earth's greatest exo-biologists.

hazards.name: Ion Storms
hazards.description: Ion storms intermittently disable Stratagems.
